text: hananim-i ileusigil adam-a geudeul-ege ileumdeul-eul illeojula ha sini geuga geudeul-ege geu ileumdeul-eul illeojumae geubunkkeseo cheonsadeul-ege i leusigil naega cheonjie issneun boiji anhneun geosgwa neohoega deuleonaegeona gam chugo issneun modeun geos-eul algo issdago neohuiege yaegihaji anhhaessneunyo
